1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 8=

3
00:00:58,960 --> 00:00:59,479
Ji Xuan.

4
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,799
Come on, take a seat.

5
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:03,799
Ji Xuan.

6
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,239
You are a lucky star for the company.

7
00:01:06,239 --> 00:01:07,959
You've only been here for two months.

8
00:01:08,519 --> 00:01:11,239
But you're much better
than many senior employees.

9
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:16,599
Look, about the scandal last time,

10
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,959
I admit I didn't handle it properly.

11
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:21,879
I even suggested you resign.

12
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:24,159
Don't take it to heart.

13
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:26,719
Mr. Li, that matter is in the past.

14
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:29,000
My only focus now is doing my job well.

15
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:32,319
Alright, try some tea.

16
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:38,760
How is it?

17
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,879
To be honest,
I'm not very good at tasting tea.

18
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,079
Ji Xuan.

19
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:47,040
I appreciate your honesty.

20
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,000
By the way,

21
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:53,400
you knew Mr. Song before, right?

22
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,760
No, I didn't.

23
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:57,719
Don't get me wrong.

24
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,680
There's a meeting in a few days.

25
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:02,400
The Song Group is the host,
and we are the organizers.

26
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:05,959
I've thought it over,
and you're the right person to go.

27
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,479
Does it have to be me?

28
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:12,159
After all, you've been interacting
with the Song Group recently.

29
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:16,479
You know
he's famously difficult to deal with.

30
00:02:16,759 --> 00:02:18,432
But you seem to get along with him well.

31
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,319
Also,

32
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,840
after the meeting,

33
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,360
I might offer you a full-time job.

34
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:28,000
Your salary will be raised.

35
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,560
Alright then, I'll go.

36
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:41,639
Here's the list
of invited guests for the meeting.

37
00:02:41,759 --> 00:02:43,960
Take a look at it.

38
00:02:45,184 --> 00:02:46,432
(List of Invited Guests for the Meeting)

39
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,000
Mr. Li.

40
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:51,800
I heard Xiao Jin has been fired
by the Rongsheng Group.

41
00:02:52,599 --> 00:02:55,240
Considering the overall interests
and potential impact,

42
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:58,520
I suggest not inviting
high-risk individuals.

43
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,840
Alright, I'll listen to you.

44
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,879
Why won't you let me attend the meeting?

45
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:18,400
Don't you feel embarrassed?

46
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,680
You've long hooked
with Song Zhaoli, right?

47
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:22,439
I could tell at the ball.

48
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,800
You've long cheated on me.

49
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:25,719
You and I are similar.

50
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:28,919
You can attend the meeting,
while I can't. Why?

51
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:32,759
Your way of clearing your name is
by smearing others.

52
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:34,719
Ji Xuan.

53
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,240
You should be grateful to me.

54
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,719
If I had slept with you,
Song Zhaoli wouldn't like you.

55
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,800
Ji Xuan, I'm telling you.

56
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:46,680
You're just Song Zhaoli's secret lover.

57
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:47,639
Let me go!

58
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,000
Xiao Jin.

59
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:56,599
Listen up,
Ji Xuan is not my secret lover.

60
00:03:57,280 --> 00:04:00,599
If she agrees to marry me now,
I'll marry her immediately.

61
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,479
Good.

62
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,920
Song Zhaoli really said that?

63
00:04:20,759 --> 00:04:23,720
Xuan, you two are a good match.

64
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:27,399
Wrong ideas will only hurt you.

65
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:34,959
Do you have no feelings
for Mr. Song at all?

66
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,279
Mr. Song.

67
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,879
Thank you for today.

68
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:48,720
Ji Xuan.

69
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:52,399
Believe it or not,
I said that not only to help you.

70
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,720
Be with me.

71
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:54,839
I'll protect you.

72
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:55,360
Mr. Song.

73
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,759
As I said before...

74
00:04:57,759 --> 00:05:00,319
I know you don't want to be
in an ambiguous relationship.

75
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,519
Neither do I.

76
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:05,319
I'm serious about what I said
in front of Xiao Jin earlier.

77
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:07,759
Mr. Song.

78
00:05:07,759 --> 00:05:08,439
Ji Xuan.

79
00:05:08,768 --> 00:05:09,270
I...

80
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:11,399
Think it over. Don't rush to say no.

81
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,199
No.

82
00:05:17,399 --> 00:05:18,519
What are you thinking about?

83
00:05:19,079 --> 00:05:20,160
Nothing.

84
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:25,480
Xuan, you're acting strangely.

85
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:27,759
No, I'm not.

86
00:05:29,504 --> 00:05:31,520
(Mom)

87
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:33,800
Mom.

88
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:35,199
Xuan, it's the weekend.

89
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,600
Bring your boyfriend home tomorrow.

90
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:40,560
Mom, I have to work
overtime this weekend.

91
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,279
So does he. Maybe another time.

92
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:45,160
You've both been working
overtime for weeks.

93
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,680
It's normal during a growth phase.

94
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,720
I'll see you the day after tomorrow.

95
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:52,000
No matter how late,
he comes over for dinner.

96
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,600
It's settled.

97
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,664
Mom.

98
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,279
What's wrong?

99
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,759
When Xiao Jin made a scene at my home,

100
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:01,360
I told my mom I had a new boyfriend.

101
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:04,480
She wants me
to bring him home this weekend.

102
00:06:08,079 --> 00:06:09,959
I actually have someone in mind.

103
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,360
Who?

104
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:33,600
Dressed in black and white?
Are you attending a funeral?

105
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,800
Why does everything you say
sound so unpleasant?

106
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,439
I'm meeting the parents tomorrow.

107
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:39,560
Can't I dress up a bit?

108
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:42,360
Xuan, your flowers.

109
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,800
Thanks, Rui.

110
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,839
My mom's been nagging me.
Sorry about this.

111
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,240
That's all right.

112
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:49,480
Actually, my family
has been pushing me too.

113
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,839
If possible,
could you see my parents next week?

114
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:53,240
We help each other.

115
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:53,879
No problem.

116
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,120
Okay.

117
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:00,959
Ji Xuan is such a nice girl.

118
00:07:01,199 --> 00:07:02,800
I can't believe she is your friend.

119
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,759
I'm killing you.

120
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,839
- Stop.
- I'm beating you.

121
00:07:09,399 --> 00:07:10,079
Don't run!

122
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,879
What did I do to deserve this?

123
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:26,439
On a weekend, I'm watching you shoot.

124
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,920
Staying in the ward all day
isn't good for you.

125
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,120
Give it a shot.

126
00:07:32,448 --> 00:07:33,040
Oh, right.

127
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:37,120
Right now, only your mouth works,
but the rest of your body doesn't.

128
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:42,480
My right hand works just fine. See?

129
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:56,429
Ji Xuan, are you free right now?

130
00:07:56,429 --> 00:07:58,279
How about coming to the archery range?

131
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:01,240
Not just with me.
Song Zhaoli is here too.

132
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,079
Come on.

133
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,160
I'm role-playing.

134
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:09,680
I'm playing Cupid,
shooting love arrows for you.

135
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,800
What happened? Someone beat you again?

136
00:08:21,399 --> 00:08:23,079
Others are perpetual runners-up.

137
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:26,199
But you? A perpetual third wheel.

138
00:08:26,439 --> 00:08:27,240
What?

139
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:33,320
Mr. Liao, I'm not free today.

140
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:36,039
I need to take my boyfriend
to meet my mom.

141
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,480
Heartbreaker.

142
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,512
Hey.

143
00:08:44,512 --> 00:08:45,039
Wait.

144
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:47,759
Wait.

145
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,840
Bring me along.

146
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:52,840
Rui,

147
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,399
just some local specialties.

148
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:56,480
I'm not sure if they suit your taste.

149
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,600
Sure. I should come often,
and I'll be used to it.

150
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,159
Okay.

151
00:09:00,399 --> 00:09:01,279
Let's eat.

152
00:09:02,960 --> 00:09:04,360
Xuan, you eat more.

153
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,879
You've gotten thin lately.

154
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:10,559
Rui.

155
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:12,759
Where do you work?

156
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:14,000
Well, I'm...

157
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,120
I'll get it.

158
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,039
Who is it?

159
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,480
Perhaps a delivery guy.

160
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,200
Just ignore him.

161
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,320
We'll just keep eating.

162
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:28,759
Mr. Song, what brings you here?

163
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:31,039
Miss Ji, aren't you going
to invite me in?

164
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:33,679
Help yourself.

165
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,039
Madam, the food is really delicious.

166
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,799
I'm glad you like it.

167
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:48,000
Who is he?

168
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,879
Hello, Mr. Song.

169
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,480
Mr. Wu.

170
00:09:55,639 --> 00:09:57,879
Madam, I work at the Song Group.

171
00:09:57,879 --> 00:10:00,240
And this is our company's president.

172
00:10:00,672 --> 00:10:01,282
Mr. Song.

173
00:10:01,282 --> 00:10:03,399
Are you here to see me?

174
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:05,320
There's an issue with your project.

175
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:07,200
I happened to see you just now.

176
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:08,759
I'll head back now.

177
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,440
Am I interrupting your dinner
with your girlfriend?

178
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,600
No, not at all.

179
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,980
Madam, Xuan.

180
00:10:18,496 --> 00:10:20,720
I'm leaving. I'll come again next week.

181
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:21,759
Alright.

182
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:23,789
Work is important.

183
00:10:23,789 --> 00:10:24,864
- Leaving now.
- Bye.

184
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:30,912
Mr. Song.

185
00:10:31,159 --> 00:10:32,600
Would you like to join us?

186
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:34,360
No, thank you. I'm leaving.

187
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,159
That guy is so inconsiderate.

188
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:50,360
He actually came here
to make Rui work on a weekend.

189
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,120
It's normal for workers in Qingcheng.

190
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,200
Let's eat.

191
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:55,360
Okay, I'll get you some soup.

192
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:08,080
- Try it.
- Okay.

193
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:11,720
How is it?

194
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,639
A bit bland, Mom.

195
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:15,600
Bland?

196
00:11:16,759 --> 00:11:18,159
I'll go add some salt.

197
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,000
What's wrong, Mom?

198
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,240
What's wrong?

199
00:11:25,056 --> 00:11:25,559
Sit down.

200
00:11:25,559 --> 00:11:26,279
I feel dizzy.

201
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:27,480
Sit down. Come on.

202
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,720
I just need some rest.

203
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,200
I'll get you some water.

204
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:42,320
Mom? What's wrong?

205
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,520
Wake up.

206
00:11:44,340 --> 00:11:44,840
Mom.

207
00:12:03,232 --> 00:12:04,000
What happened?

208
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:24,602
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

209
00:12:24,762 --> 00:12:26,642
♪Flickering neon lights♪

210
00:12:26,842 --> 00:12:30,170
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

211
00:12:30,682 --> 00:12:32,954
♪Every star is♪

212
00:12:33,242 --> 00:12:37,114
♪My heartbeat for you♪

213
00:12:38,426 --> 00:12:40,250
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

214
00:12:40,410 --> 00:12:41,962
♪And land in your arms♪

215
00:12:42,362 --> 00:12:45,818
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

216
00:12:46,074 --> 00:12:48,634
♪In the blue sky♪

217
00:12:48,698 --> 00:12:52,826
♪Your smile still lingers♪

218
00:12:53,754 --> 00:12:57,402
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

219
00:12:57,658 --> 00:13:01,322
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

220
00:13:01,530 --> 00:13:04,442
♪Can't find a cure♪

221
00:13:04,442 --> 00:13:08,954
♪To love you after we've parted♪

222
00:13:09,146 --> 00:13:13,178
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

223
00:13:13,178 --> 00:13:17,042
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

224
00:13:17,042 --> 00:13:18,842
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

225
00:13:18,938 --> 00:13:24,090
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

226
00:13:24,730 --> 00:13:28,442
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

227
00:13:28,634 --> 00:13:31,386
♪Can't find a cure♪

228
00:13:31,514 --> 00:13:36,154
♪To love you after we've parted♪

229
00:13:36,322 --> 00:13:40,090
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

230
00:13:40,314 --> 00:13:43,898
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

231
00:13:44,122 --> 00:13:46,162
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

232
00:13:46,162 --> 00:13:51,162
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
